Nathan Lovejoy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nathan_Lovejoy 0 Nathan Lovejoy (born 2 December 1981) is an Australian actor, best known for his role as Borkman in the Australian comedy series Sammy J Randy in Ricketts Lane, for which he was nominated for an AACTA Award for Best Performance in a Television Comedy.He also appeared as Felix Rolleston in the TV movie The Mystery of a Hansom Cab. and Will Sharp in season 2 of ABC political thriller The Code.
